title: The Doc Love Radio Show (TDLRS) - 2015
description:
There you go guy...
10 years worth of Radio Shows,
15 years worth of Articles
System Audio,
multiple seasons of 5th segments
and to top it off
multiple seasons of Advanced System Class.

If you don't get and keep The Right One, well than it's your fault,
you have all the material you need right here.


Remember it's a numbers' game,
she'll do it with whom she'll want...
It may as well be you.

P.S.: If someone asks you for a love advice, tell him to go to doclove.com. Only after he agrees he'll stick to The System you tell him (let him download for himself) about this secret place.

P.P.S.: No comments welcome this time, as this is my LAST upload. Thank you.

I also won't be seeding all this stuff all the time, so it's up to you community member to seed it.

And don't ask me to connect all the dots if you don't understand something.

P.P.P.S.: HNY 2016
